column2: select z.*,    p.petrorad_u, p.petroraderr_u, p.petrorad_g, p.petroraderr_g, p.petrorad_r, p.petroraderr_r, p.petrorad_i, p.petroraderr_i, p.petrorad_z, p.petroraderr_z,    p.petromag_u, p.petromagerr_u, p.petromag_g, p.petromagerr_g, p.petromag_r, p.petromagerr_r, p.petromag_i, p.petromagerr_i, p.petromag_z, p.petromagerr_z,   p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z,   s.z into mydb.dist_all from zoo2MainSpecz z   join   photoobjall p on p.specobjid=z.specobjid   join   specobjall s on s.specobjid=z.specobjid where   z.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_disturbed_debiased > z.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_irregular_debiased   and   z.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_disturbed_debiased > #   and    z.t0#_odd_feature_a2#_disturbed_flag <> #
